        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 3 at 8:27PM MDT by NWS Denver CO</headline>
        <description>At 827 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 6
miles southwest of Hugo, or 14 miles southeast of Limon, moving
northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible. Hail may
accumulate on roadways causing hazardous travel.

Locations impacted include...
Hugo.
</description>
        <instruction>Monitor the weather situation closely and be alert for threatening
weather conditions.</instruction>
